<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:13.5pt"><strong><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">作品引用</span></strong><strong><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> &lt;cite&gt;</span></strong></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&lt;cite&gt;</span></strong></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">表示一个作品的引用，且必须包含作品的标题。这个引用可能是一个根据适当的上下文约定关联引用的元数据的缩写。</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"></span></span><br></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&lt;cite&gt;
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">标签通常表示它所包含的文本对某个参考文献的引用，比如书籍或者杂志的标题。</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"></span></span><br></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">按照惯例，引用的文本将以斜体显示。</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"></span></span><br></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">用</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> &lt;cite&gt;
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">标签把指向其他文档的引用分离出来，尤其是分离那些传统媒体中的文档，如书籍、杂志、期刊，等等。如果引用的这些文档有联机版本，还应该把引用包括在一个</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> &lt;a&gt;
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">标签中，从而把一个超链接指向该联机版本。</span></span></li>
</ul>
